OL,3,CMan jailed after raping 13-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl on Boxing Day
OL,6,FA Guernsey man has been jailed for 15
OL,7,Fyears and five months after committing
OL,8,Fa series of sexual offences, including
OL,9,Fraping a 13-year-old girl he met on
OL,10,Fsocial media.
OL,12,FBen Frank Spruce, 20, was found guilty
OL,13,Fof two counts of rape - as well as two
OL,14,Fcounts of sexual touching of a child
OL,15,Fand one count of sexual assault,
OL,16,Finvolving two other schoolgirls -
OL,17,Ffollowing a two-and-a-half week trial
OL,18,Fat the Royal Court in March.
