OL,3,CMan jailed after raping 13-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl on Boxing Day
OL,6,FThe Court heard how Spruce sent a 13-
OL,7,Fyear-old girl unsolicited, explicit
OL,8,Fpictures and repeatedly asked her to
OL,9,Fdo the same while also pressuring her
OL,10,Fto meet in person.
OL,12,FShe met Spruce on 26 December 2023 in
OL,13,Ffields near the old Castel Hospital
OL,14,Fand refused sexual contact but was
OL,15,Fforcefully raped twice.
OL,17,FThe girl says she felt scared and
OL,18,Fdisgusted, adding that she now freezes
OL,19,Fif a boy accidentally touches her.
