OL,3,CMan jailed after raping 13-year-old
OL,4,Cgirl on Boxing Day
OL,6,FThe defendant denied messaging or
OL,7,Fmeeting the girl but after Spruce's
OL,8,Fphone was seized in January in an
OL,9,Funrelated search, police found his
OL,10,Flocation history placed him close to
OL,11,Fthe scene on the day of the assaults.
OL,13,FA used condom was also discovered by
OL,14,Fpolice in the field, with strong
OL,15,Fforensic evidence tying it to Spruce.
OL,17,FSpruce also sexually touched a 14-year-
OL,18,Fold girl around the lanes at Beau
OL,19,FSejour multiple times between October
OL,20,F2022 and January 2023.
