OL,6,FAgain, Spruce claimed he did not know
OL,7,Fher but the Court heard he used social
OL,8,Fmedia to pressure the girl to meet in
OL,9,Fperson, with her saying that Spruce
OL,10,Ftold her to "come or you'll make it
OL,11,Fworse for yourself".
OL,13,FSeparately, Spruce sexually assaulted
OL,14,Fa 15-year-old girl at Sausmaurez Park
OL,15,Fin January 2023 - he claims he thought
OL,16,Fit was someone else.
