OL,6,FHe also pled guilty to six separate
OL,7,Fcounts of misuse of
OL,8,Ftelecommunications, three counts of
OL,9,Fsexual touching of a child, and four
OL,10,Fcounts of making indecent images.
OL,12,FThese offences included Spruce
OL,13,Fmessaging children in Jersey, England,
OL,14,Fand the Isle of Man - asking for and
OL,15,Fsending nude pictures.
OL,17,FOn one occasion, he asked a boy to
OL,18,Fsend an explicit image and then sent
OL,19,Fit to the boy's friends.
