OL,6,FThe counts of sexual touching and
OL,7,Fmaking indecent images involve Spruce
OL,8,Fhaving sex with a girl and recording
OL,9,Fthe incident on his phone - the pleas
OL,10,Fof sexual touching were accepted
OL,11,Finstead of rape as consent was not
OL,12,Fclear.
OL,14,FOne of Spruce's victims said the
OL,15,Fimpact of his actions "will live with
OL,16,Fme forever", another said, "I worry
OL,17,Fthat he will come and find me".
