OL,6,FFollowing sentencing, Detective
OL,7,FInspector Ian Tanner from Guernsey
OL,8,FPolice's Public Protection Unit said:
OL,9,F"Our officers are committed to
OL,10,Frelentlessly pursuing those who seek
OL,11,Fto exploit young people in our
OL,12,Fcommunity, working tirelessly to
OL,13,Fsecure convictions.
OL,15,F"Along with this, our partners in
OL,16,FHealth & Social Care, Education, and
OL,17,Fthe third sector work tirelessly to
OL,18,Fsupport young people who have been
OL,19,Fvictim to these horrific crimes."
